review: I love Chilis!!! Every time I go there not only is the menu filled with great choices the atmosphere and people are cool.  I love the spinach dip is keeps me coming back for more. The two can dine is the best choices of any ones around. My friends and I can be on a budget and still enjoy everything Chilis has to offer.
This Chili's is not were you say it is. In fact there is  Chili's in this town. The phone connects to an AutoZone. Sorry!
